Starting with :
VS Code Settings
go to Extension

1. Need to install "Prettier-Code formatter" enable it. After that refresh the vs code
2. Need to install a color theme " One Monokai Theme " set color theme.

Go to Settings

1. Search default formatter> set to "Prettier-Code formatter"
2. Search format on save > check the checkbox
3. Search auto save > set to "on focus change"
4. Search tab size > set to "2"
5. Search auto closing tags > uncheck (if u want to close the tag manually)

